## Key Security Improvements

- **Login brute-force protection**: 5 attempts/min per identifier
- **NoSQL injection prevention**: All `$regex` inputs escaped
- **OTP crypto-secure**: `crypto.randomInt()` replaces `Math.random()`
- **Email verification enforced**: Registration requires verified OTP
- **Security headers**: HSTS, X-Frame-Options, nosniff, Referrer-Policy, Permissions-Policy
- **No error leaks**: Internal error details no longer sent to clients
- **Pending student API block**: Middleware rejects unapproved students from API access

## Verification

- `npx tsc --noEmit` → **0 new errors** (2 pre-existing in test file only)

